text: Yongning Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Zengcheng District, Guangzhou, Guangdong, China. , it has 8 residential communities and 22 villages under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Guangdong == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Guangdong Category:Guangzhou
